Steps to install a MEAN stack OUTLINE

A. Create GCloud Instance

  Common to all applications:
    sudo apt-get update
    sudo apt-get build-essential apt-transport-https ca-certificates
    
B. Install MongoDB
  sudo apt-get install mongodb
  mongod status
  
C. Install NodeJS
  sudo apt-get install nodejs npm
  
  sudo npm init
  

D. Install Angular
  sudo npm install -g @angular/cli

E. Install Express

F. Firewall

